desc: Much more than Bangkok and sunburnt farangs (the Thai term for Western tourists, which translates to guava), modern Thailand is boundlessly captivating and diverse. You`ll not want to miss out on the irresistible beaches and hotels for which the country is rightly renowned. However, we suggest that curious travellers always delve a little deeper too. Rural lodges, remote mountains and small, community-run tourism ventures can reveal a side to Thailand that most travellers don't know exists.\n We at Experience Travel Group have had a firm foothold in Thailand since its earliest days and excel in searching out the hidden gems. Talk to us about how we can challenge your perceptions of this exceptional country.
